social_posts.post_text: So great to be a part of this show! Premiere of @paultgoldmanseries @peacocktv Catch this unique style of storytelling and jump on the ride this January!  #peacock #sethrogen #rosannaarquette #deewallace #jasonwoliner #paultgoldman #premiere #caviar #lionsgate

Wow! What a unique once in a lifetime experience to be a #distinguishedvisitor on the U.S.S. Abraham Lincon (CVN 72) !! I had the opportunity to spend two days and a night aboard this incredible vessel with a group of 11 amazingly kind diverse people from all different fields. I got first-hand experience, witnessing the awesome power and discipline that  The Navy Air Force brings to the table when protecting this great country. Thank you for this memory that will never fade and will always be with me! Much respect and thanks to the men and women that serve and keep us all safe everyday! #thenavyexperience #flynavy Thank you Steven Fiebing for setting this all up. And thank you Steve from #rockandrollfantasycamp and Britt for the introduction to this experience. #usmilitary #respect #strength #usa #protect #ussabrahamlincoln #ussabrahamlincolncvn72 #kindtraveler #yr
